{
  "stem": "322.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First-- well, of course, it was not all on one shot, you know, from-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a lot of Auschwitz transports on foot ended up in Gleiwitz.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then from Gleiwitz, we ended up in Blechhammer, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then from Blechhammer to Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Finally-- and that was a three-week march-- from Gross-Rosen, we were put into open cattle cars and transported to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But Otto Moll was-- he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he became in charge of another concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a concentration camp, by the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was caught in 1946 as a prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No, I'm sorry-- no, it was in-- he was, he was caught, perhaps, late 1945, put in a prison camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then he was tried-- I believe he was tried in Dachau-- convicted, and then executed right there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They hung him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To me-- I ended up in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I arrived in Buchenwald February the 10th.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Very shortly after that, I, I contracted typhus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, I was only maybe one or two days, the most three days, in the upper level of Buchenwald, which was a political prison and whatever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It also had-- it had a sort of a, a-- well, it had some sort of hospital of some sort.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they found that I had typhus, they transferred me to the little camp, which was the death section of Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there were primarily Jews there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were some non-Jews there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were dying there like flies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't think that, that most anyone that was put in there lasted longer than maybe five or 10 days, And I don't know how I was able to survive there until April the 11th, 1945.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I was not assigned to any work, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
